g.text: Scan QR Code from Node.js terminal
Select a chat from the list
App sends messages to Python backend for processing
Login with Phone, Code, and Password
Select a chat from the list
App sends request to Python backend
Backend processes data, generates profile, and creates FAISS memory
User types and sends text message
Backend performs RAG search and gets LLM reply
User records and sends voice message
App calls `/chat` endpoint with audio file
Backend transcribes audio (Whisper), performs RAG, gets LLM reply
App displays user's transcribed message and bot's text reply
User records voice input in Call Screen
App calls `/call` endpoint with audio file
Backend performs full loop: STT -> RAG -> LLM -> TTS
App plays voice reply to user
